  "img": "icons/skills/social/diplomacy-handshake.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You magically emanate a sense of friendship toward one creature you can see within range. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or have the &amp;Reference[Charmed] condition for the duration. The target succeeds automatically if it isn't a Humanoid, if you're fighting it, or if you have cast this spell on it within the past 24 hours.</p><p>The spell ends early if the target takes damage or if you make an attack roll, deal damage, or force anyone to make a saving throw. When the spell ends, the target knows it was Charmed by you.</p><p>The verbal component of this spell may be slipped into casual conversation. A successful [[/check ability=wis skill=ins]] check contested by your [[/check ability=cha skill=dec]] check (made with advantage) allows a listener to determine that a spell has been cast.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
